11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_NS_QUANTILE_NOISE_ESTIMATOR_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_NS_QUANTILE_NOISE_ESTIMATOR_H_
13
14#include <math.h>
15#include <array>
16
17#include "api/array_view.h"
18#include "modules/audio_processing/ns/ns_common.h"
19
20namespace webrtc {
21
22constexpr int kSimult = 3;
23
24// For quantile noise estimation.
25class QuantileNoiseEstimator {
26 public:
27 QuantileNoiseEstimator();
28 QuantileNoiseEstimator(const QuantileNoiseEstimator&) = delete;
29 QuantileNoiseEstimator& operator=(const QuantileNoiseEstimator&) = delete;
30
31 // Estimate noise.
32 void Estimate(rtc::ArrayView<const float, kFftSizeBy2Plus1> signal_spectrum,
33 rtc::ArrayView<float, kFftSizeBy2Plus1> noise_spectrum);
34
35 private:
36 std::array<float, kSimult * kFftSizeBy2Plus1> density_;
37 std::array<float, kSimult * kFftSizeBy2Plus1> log_quantile_;
38 std::array<float, kFftSizeBy2Plus1> quantile_;
39 std::array<int, kSimult> counter_;
40 int num_updates_ = 1;
41};
42
43} // namespace webrtc
44
45#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_NS_QUANTILE_NOISE_ESTIMATOR_H_
